      "content": "i'm just really stressed out and i can't afford to go back to the doctor right this second. if i just take half the dose of the diazepam and have that one glass of wine, isn't that basically the same as just taking a slightly stronger dose of the pill? it seems like a lot of drama for just one glass of wine.",
